OL,6,FAn ad for Transport for London's new
OL,7,F'Act Like a Friend' campaign has been
OL,8,Fbanned for reinforcing negative
OL,9,Fstereotypes about black men.
OL,11,FThe Facebook ad, part of the campaign
OL,12,Fthat encourages people to intervene
OL,13,Fsafely if they witness sexual
OL,14,Fharassment or hate crime on the TfL
OL,15,Fnetwork, showed a black male verbally
OL,16,Fharassing a young girl accompanied by
OL,17,Fa white male friend, who sat down
OL,18,Fclose to the victim 'boxing her in'.
