OL,6,FA viewer complained that the ad was
OL,7,Firresponsible, harmful and offensive
OL,8,Ffor perpetuating negative racial
OL,9,Fstereotypes about black teenage boys.
OL,11,FTfL told the Advertising Standards
OL,12,FAuthority (ASA) that both characters
OL,13,Fintimidated the victim and displayed
OL,14,Foffensive behaviour.
