OL,3,CTfL ad banned for reinforcing negative
OL,4,Cstereotypes about black men
OL,6,FThe ad was one of three made for
OL,7,Fsocial media which had been cut from a
OL,8,Ftwo-minute 'Act Like a Friend'
OL,9,Ffilm.The two other cut-downs featured
OL,10,Fa white male committing a hate crime
OL,11,Fagainst a black woman and a white male
OL,12,Fcommitting a hate crime against
OL,13,Fanother white male.
OL,15,FTfL said that a typical member of the
OL,16,FFacebook audience would have been
OL,17,Fserved any combination of the campaign
OL,18,Fads three times, and estimated that
OL,19,Fthe probability of a person seeing
OL,20,Fonly the cut-down that was the subject
OL,21,Fof the complaint to be around 2%.
