OL,3,CTfL ad banned for reinforcing negative
OL,4,Cstereotypes about black men
OL,6,FTfL said they used a bespoke casting
OL,7,Fdiversity tracker to ensure they were
OL,8,Frepresentative of London's population
OL,9,Facross all their campaigns.
OL,11,FThe ASA said it was possible to see
OL,12,Fthe ad in isolation.
OL,14,FIt said: "We understood there was a
OL,15,Fnegative racial stereotype based on
OL,16,Fthe association between black males,
OL,17,Fincluding teenagers, and threatening
OL,18,Fbehaviour. We assessed whether the ad
OL,19,Freinforced that stereotype.
