OL,6,FA TfL spokeswoman said: "Our aim is to
OL,7,Fensure that our advertising reflects
OL,8,FLondon's diverse population and does
OL,9,Fnot perpetuate any stereotypes, just
OL,10,Fas we ensure that our services are as
OL,11,Ffair, accessible and inclusive as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"We're sorry that this social media
OL,15,Fadvert ` a shortened version of the
OL,16,Ffull two-minute advert that includes a
OL,17,Fdiverse range of ethnicities ` falls
OL,18,Fbelow our usual high standards when
OL,19,Fviewed in isolation.
