OL,7,Fthis shortened advert in isolation, we
OL,8,Fare committed to upholding the ASA's
OL,9,Fstandards for all of our campaigns and
OL,10,Fare no longer using this shortened
OL,11,Fadvert in our ongoing campaign to
OL,12,Fencourage people to support other
OL,13,Fpassengers targeted by hate crime,
OL,14,Fsexual offences and harassment on our
OL,15,Ftransport network."
